{"k":"GoogleMaps-MarkerMenu","t":"實作 Google Maps 右鍵選單","i":"2015-11-05","a":[{"e":"p","s":[{"e":"span","t":"此作品主要在於開發出可以在 Google Maps 上面編輯基本路徑的功能，利用 "},{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/?hl=zh-tw","target":"_blank"},"t":"Google Maps JavaScript API"},{"e":"span","t":" 設計出規劃路線的工具，並且可以匯出路間經緯度 "},{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://products.office.com/zh-tw/excel","target":"_blank"},"t":"Excel"},{"e":"span","t":"。"}]},{"e":"p","s":[{"e":"span","t":"在 Google Maps 上顯示選單，主要是使用 "},{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/events?hl=zh-tw","target":"_blank"},"t":"Google Maps JavaScript Events"},{"e":"span","t":" 來實作，並且搭配 "},{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/markers","target":"_blank"},"t":"Marker"},{"e":"span","t":"、"},{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/examples/polyline-simple?hl=zh-tw","target":"_blank"},"t":"Polyline"},{"e":"span","t":" 來繪製出路線圖，並且針對 Marker 綁定 Event 來實作 "},{"e":"b","t":"刪除節點"},{"e":"span","t":" 的功能。"}]},{"e":"p","s":[{"e":"span","t":"此實作中有一項特別的技巧，就是在 Ployline 上點擊滑鼠右鍵時，必須要可以 插入節點 的功能，難點是在於 Maps 上的 "},{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/examples/control-positioning?hl=zh-tw","target":"_blank"},"t":"Google Maps Position"},{"e":"span","t":" 與 "},{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/examples/icon-complex","target":"_blank"},"t":"Google Maps Point"},{"e":"span","t":" 物件的"},{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://github.com/comdan66/OA-googleMapsMenu/blob/master/js/public.js#L51","target":"_blank"},"t":"轉換"},{"e":"span","t":"，必須將點擊位置的經緯度經計算後得知在地圖元素上相對應的 left、top 數值，再將選單顯示在該位置上。"}]},{"e":"p","t":"因為要針對不同區段的 Polyline 監聽 Event，所以必須使用特別的方式去畫出 Polyline，目前我所使用的方法是將 Markers 之間用單個 Polyline 做連接，所以地圖上 Polyline 的數量會是 Marker 的 n-1 個，如此一來就可以對每段 Polyline 監聽 Event 了！"},{"e":"p","t":"當插入節點時，便可以取出該 Polyline 是位於哪兩個 Markers 之間，這時候再針對陣列去做橋接，重組後的 Markers 陣列再重新繪製一次 Polyline 即可！"}],"r":[{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://works.ioa.tw/OA-googleMapsMenu/index.html","target":"_blank"},"t":"Live Demo"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://github.com/comdan66/OA-googleMapsMenu","target":"_blank"},"t":"GitHub 原始碼"}]}]}],"g":["Google Maps","JavaScript"]}